values:
Bear VS. Shark. 


And I only missed them by eight months...

Ehhhh. 

 The first full day of HS wasn't too bad, I guess. I saw Danny in the morning (two hugs!) and Will in the afternoon (phonenumber!), and also Cooper (hug!<3) around that time, so that made me happy. 

BUT. My bus was nearly an hour late (and the fucker doesn't get us to school until almost 8:30 every day) so I just got a ride home from Katie. 

And I have four books for English; I'm having to use my brother's old bookbag just to fit everything in it. 

I guess I lied: FIRST DAY=Sucktastic!

I am having trouble sleeping, and nightmares now.


I always die at the end. 

Or they are very graphic and violent. 

It's disturbing.

First day of High School.

I'm overwhelmed/stressed out/panicked. 

I have two assigments due monday: essay and journal entry. 

This semester should be loads of fun.
